Father, we thank You, Lord. Thank You for the rain we received tonight, Lord.

02:20:26.010 --> 02:20:29.357
Thank You for the thunder. Thank You for the lightning. Thank You for the blessing.

02:20:29.358 --> 02:20:47.464
Cleaning our air, cleaning things, getting ready for a beautiful summer that's coming.

02:20:47.465 --> 02:21:00.610
I know it's been a long time. We'll pray again tomorrow, but I just pause because I'm trying to filter as we grow.

02:21:00.611 --> 02:21:06.559
I thought it was great. You did? Yeah, I thought it was wonderful. Okay. Well, you're always there for me, honey.

02:21:06.560 --> 02:21:15.222
I want to get to that level when you're praying and I'm seeing over what I'm seeing, and I don't know.

02:21:15.223 --> 02:21:20.649
I felt the flow when I was in the river. All right. Well, we love you.

02:21:20.650 --> 02:21:28.073
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. We'll see you tomorrow. God bless you all. Have a wonderful night. Bye-bye.

